<ab facs="#facs_82_r2l16">ledig werden müg Eʒ ſeẏ <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> / daʒ der <expan>egen<ex>ante</ex></expan> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> Burger </ab>
